   File        : ClassDetailPageV2.razor
   Namespace   : AbsenceApp.Client.Modules.Classes
   Author      : Michael
   Version     : 1.1.1
   Created     : 2026-03-21
   Updated     : 2026-04-04
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Purpose     : V2 Class detail page. Displays a single class record using the
                 V2 PageTemplateV2 primitive instead of deprecated DetailPageV2
                 and DetailSectionV2. Delegates data loading to
                 ClassDetailViewModelV2.
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Changes     :
     - 1.0.0  2026-03-21  Initial implementation (Phase 7).
     - 1.0.1  2026-03-25  Removed invalid V2 component imports.
     - 1.1.0  2026-03-26  Replaced DetailPageV2 + DetailSectionV2 with
                          PageTemplateV2. Updated namespace and layout.
                          Preserved all ViewModel logic and UI structure.
     - (bumped)  2026-04-04  Phase 3 Stabilisation Issue 2: changed @layout from BaseLayoutV2 to MainLayoutV2 so all module pages use the canonical V2 shell layout with correct fixed-header padding.
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Notes       :
     - Route: /v2/classes/{Id:long}
     - Register ClassDetailViewModelV2 as Scoped in Phase 10.
